 <text>
  <front>
   <head>IN A LETTER to A.R.C. ON HER WISHING TO BE CALLED ANNA.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">FORGIVE me, if I wound your ear,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">By calling of you Nancy,</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Which is the name of my sweet friend,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">The other's but her fancy.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Ah, dearest girl! how could your mind</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">The strange distinction frame?</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">The whimsical, unjust caprice,</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Which robs you of your name.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">agrees with what we see,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">A being wild and airy;</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Gay as a nymph of Flora's train,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Fantastic as a fairy.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="4" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">But  of a different kind,</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">A melancholy maid;</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Boasting a sentimental soul,</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">In solemn pomp array'd.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="5" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="17" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Oh ne'er will forsake the sound,</l>
     <l n="18" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">So artless and so free!</l>
     <l n="19" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Be what you will with all mankind.</l>
     <l n="20" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">But , still with me.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
